LET ME INTRODUCE MYSELF...Hi my name is Rita.  My clients call me Reiki Rita.  I am an Intuitive Energy Healer, Teacher and Certified Life Coach.  I am highly regarded for the work I do in the Holistic-Health industry offering over 10+ years of experience.  Although Reiki heals on all levels of our physical, mental, emotional and spiritual health, I am highly specialized in the area of emotional healing.  Mainly because our emotions determine the root of our physical health!  I am an advocate for protecting the rights of the "vulnerable" (especially of children) and will continue to inspire healthy, positive change in people, our environment and humanity in general!  Don't you think it's time we took our power back!  My philosophy is when we keep encouraging the way people think and behave in a loving and positive way - we can change the world for the better - one person at a time!MY PASSIONI feel priviledged to have an opportunity to reach out to you personally and ask for your support in backing my book project.  This is my first book and another to follow that I am very excited to share with you at a later date as well.  The idea for the book started over 6 years ago with me journaling my feelings in order to heal and "reparent" myself from my dysfunctional family.  My journaling resulted in two book. Parents with Price Tags is the first and will launch this March and the other on conquering fear and raising your a healthy self esteem will release late 2014 (if I can raise the necessary funding -- with your help!).  "Parents With Price Tags" will inspire global change.  It goes where no other book has with respect to uncovering many of the common concerns many families experience and why they exist.  In this book you will learn to - 
recognize many common family problems and why they exist;
identify issues in your family, understand why and how they affect you, and learn healthier alternatives to family life;
replace feelings of fear and hopelessness with feelings of love and hope;
stop being controlled and take control of your own life;
find self-love and self-respect;
embrace your true self; and 
find the courage to live the life you deserve by taking the necessary steps that will change your life and lead you to inner peace and genuine happiness - GUILT FREE!
PROGRESS OF THE BOOK?  Both books are written. "Parents with Price Tags" is in the final editing of the manuscript, ready to move to design, publishing and then printing.  Second book still needs professional editing, design and publishing.......Here's why I need your support in order to make these books available to you and others...As a single mom with 3 children and a business to run, I honestly had no idea that I would be guided to write a book, let alone two of them or how much money it involves.  So that is why I am reaching out to you for your generous support in order to to make this happen!  I truly believe you or someone you love will see real value in the content of these books...MY VISION FOR OUR FUTURE?  To raise our children on purpose and with purpose!  I would also like to create a Parenting Life Skill Program that will prepare people for the realties of modern parenthood in the 21st Century.  If your generous support surpasses $10,000, I can make this a reality!THOUGHT??  If we can put forth a conscious effort to improve our economy, preserve our wildlife, and protect our rain forests, don't you think it's time we saved our precious children?Other Ways You Can Help?I realize that some of you may not be in a financial position to help me right now.  You are what I call wealthy in spirit but poor in cash.  But, there is still ways you can help out:

HELP SPREAD THE WORD - twitter, facebook, pinterest, linked in, or instigram the message to everyone you know.  
Please use the Indiegogo share tools available to you to make a little noise and help heal the world!
My deepest gratitude for your help and your kind generosity!namaste, Reiki Rita
